{"tid":131912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[猶太犬？] 總幫辦及2警員已上訴推翻定罪及判刑！！","createTime":"2017-02-23T11:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T11:59:18.000Z","uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f66d252cf99e09e5b4774d7f9e592ac736f053e","tid":131912,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:50:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=Nl%2Bce6%2FxXxAB2W4e8qnvdviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=f5a21c5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a><br />\n<br />\n七名警務人員襲擊前公民黨成員曾健超罪成，上周五(17日)各被判入獄兩年。律政司發言人今日(23日)表示，本周一(20日)收到第一、第四及第七被告，即總督察黃祖成、警員劉興沛及黃偉豪三人，就定罪及刑期提出上訴的上訴通知書。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n七名被告依次是有組織及三合會調查科(俗稱O記)總督察黃祖成(48歲)、觀塘反黑組高級督察劉卓毅(29歲)、觀塘反黑組偵緝警長白榮斌(42歲)、觀塘反黑組警員劉興沛(38歲)、東九龍總區偵緝警員陳少丹(33歲)、九龍城偵緝警員關嘉豪(32歲)，及觀塘反黑組偵緝警員黃偉豪(36歲)。&nbsp;<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f0299226f832f18777087bd41ac3845a6ff0f655","tid":131912,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/195804_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F195804_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=6961af25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0db7e2c11239606a80d15dddefc02ff297466434","tid":131912,"uid":4360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:59:18.000Z","msg":"有冇機會上訴完仲判重手d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}